<plot>'Scarecrow' tells the story of a farmer who is too old to do his job on the farm and a scarecrow too friendly to keep the rabbits away from the prized pumpkins. Yet, in trying to solve their own problems they end up inadvertently solving each other's. 'Scarecrow' is a beautiful, charming tale about finding one's own way that all ages are sure to enjoy.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?479768</url></doc>
